            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Data of the monitor detector were used to normalize",
                "the count rates of the telescopes for the target",
                "thickness and beam intensity to obtain absolute",
                "differential cross-sections. The relative cross-",
                "section data of the telescopes in the flat region of",
                "forward angles was normalized to unity."
              ]
            }
          ],
