          "ANALYSIS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "INTAD"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " In order to determine the cross-sections of",
                "PLFs, the plots of 2*pi*sin(thetaCM)*(d(sigma)/",
                "d(omega))CM vs thetaCM were approximated as Gaussian",
                "distributions. The fitted Gaussian curves were",
                "integrated from 0 - 180 degree to obtain cross-sections",
                "of PLFs which is plotted in Fig. 3 against Z=3-8.",
                "GAUSSIAN function used for fitting is:(Area/(2*pi*sigma",
                "*sigma))*exp(((x-x0)*(x- x0))/(2*pi*sigma*sigma))"
              ]
            }
